title: Migrate password out of Firefox lockwise without sync... Is that possible?
content: A few weeks ago I mistakenly delete a few password on firefox passwords, and that passes through sync fast. Now I still have one dormant iOS device (not connected to net) with (no longer on shelf) Firefox lockwise. Are there anyway I can export that, or at least prevent sync? Is that password stored anywhere as a file that can be accessed?
creator: youranshen.official
